Bamigbola Gbolagunte, Akure Unknown gunmen have reportedly abducted three travellers in Ikakumo in Ose Local Government Area of Ondo state. The travellers were said to have been abducted in the town which is the boundary between Ondo and Edo States. A source hinted that a commercial motorcyclist popularly called okara rider who ran into the scene was beaten to stupor by the suspects. The commercial motorcyclist reportedly fainted and was later resuscitated before he narrated the incident to the residents. The Ikare-Akoko police area commander, Mr Razak Rauf who confirmed the incident, assured that the hoodlums who kidnapped the travellers will soon be apprehended. He said the police have commenced investigation into the matter. 